title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1990-02-25
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Jack A Roe, Little Red Rooster, Stagger Lee, Queen Jane Approximately, The Last Time, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, A Little Light, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Wharf Rat-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text:
Recording review Like most audience recordings, give yourself a couple of songs to become acclimated to the recording and you'll start to discover it's true nature.

This recording is inviting and gets out of the way so that you can enjoy the performance of the evening.  Everything is there; vocals, drums, keys, bass, audience, vibe, energy, synergy.

Enjoyable. Thank you for your time and effort to put this together.
